page.title: 20Credits
page.content: {Roderick Watt}wrote the following pages:"A keeper's life in Assynt","The Assynt Shoot","Farming in Inchnadamph" "Fishing in Inchnadamph" &"Law and Order in Inchnadamph" and"Ruins of Inchnadamph".{ {Rory MacGregor}wrote "Inchnadamph Community","Assynt Sheepdog Trials", "School in Inchnadamph" ,"Assynt Mountain Rescue Team","Inchnadamph Lodge","Employment in Inchnadamph", "Inchnadamph Nature Reserve" and "Birdlife in Inchnadamph". {Sharon Macdonald }wrote "Inchnadamph Church","Amenities in Inchnadamph" and "Inchnadamph Hotel".{ {Heather Macgregor}wrote "A Shepherd's Daughter's Day" and "A Woman's life in Inchnadamph".
